In microwave-safe bowl, microwave corn syrup for 1 minute or until it boils. Stir in peanut butter. Gently add KELLOGG'S CRISPIX cereal, stirring until well coated. Spread mixture onto waxed paper lined or greased 10x15-inch pan. In microwave-safe bowl, microwave chocolate on medium for 45 seconds or until melted. Drizzle chocolate over mixture. Chill. Break into bite-size pieces. Store in airtight container.